@topomotorsports did an amazing job customizing my @fordbronco . We made a great bumper from scratch. Utilizing the frame for the tire and tire wrack weight. The spare tire is no longer sitting on the swing gate door. The engineering with this rear replacement bumper is incredible. Still utilizing stock bumper sensors. The Rock sliders work perfect and look great. I put it through the test and it held up. Thank again guys over @topomotorsports . If you’re interested in this rear bumper go check out www.topomotorsports.com.
